"@Ore-O":/dis/the-time-wasting-thread/post/54e0262463687211d4a70000#post_54e0262463687211d4a70000
[bq="Ore-O"]So, Sponge out of Water. It is out now.[/bq]
It's a good movie. It's basically a great episode of Spongebob stretched to ninety minutes. And while it's not as good as the first Spongebob movie (because frankly that's asking for the impossible) it's funny, cute, and inoffensive. You could do waaaaaaay worse than Sponge Out of Water.
